{"tid":141533,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"認真問三星手機","createTime":"2017-03-03T04:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T11:09:13.000Z","uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27c12e57bceaef4c075f32d76b39a8256ef69a80","tid":141533,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ov67p514\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fov67p514&h=4569ce1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姪女部A7<br />\n用左一年多小小，剛過保養<br />\n前幾日佢叉完電<br />\n一攞起部電話<br />\n即時辣親加電到隻手<br />\n原來叉電位上面燶哂加漏電<br />\n(用原裝叉機加線)<br />\n<br />\n我約左下星期上三星維修<br />\n上到去應該點話好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上黎請教下巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f479e436ad6ef80d3d73a9ef8ec9685c17ca46","tid":141533,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"最好搵多兩個大隻fd上去，唔打得都睇得"},{"pid":"3f4d0832ce8e0bd3e71bd811663b58db6fba955e","tid":141533,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好搵多兩個大隻fd上去，唔打得都睇得</blockquote><br />\n我單拖咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d91ca730148af4fadef9c115df91fb83f2ef9c1","tid":141533,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fda17924fdd51b1554136fd93d5f1fcf603122a","tid":141533,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"call報紙啦<br />\n<br />\n***仲賣行哂廣告講安全...得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27977ad5fb71bf6d929b9841e1c5c8388ccfda24","tid":141533,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>call報紙啦<br />\n<br />\n***仲賣行哂廣告講安全...得